<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>NumBite</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/header") %>

    <main class="home-container">
      <div class="welcome-desc">
        <p>Craving a quick snack of trivia? You're in the right place. 🍪</p>

        <p>
          Here at NumBite, every number has a story — whether it's your
          birthdate, a random digit, or today’s date. We fetch fascinating, fun,
          and sometimes downright weird facts about numbers from the Numbers
          API, just for you.
        </p>

        <p>
          🔢 Enter a number, click a button, and get a tasty bite of
          knowledge.<br />🎲 Feeling spontaneous? Try a random number and see
          where it takes you.
        </p>

        <p>
          Go ahead — explore the hidden side of numbers.<br />Because at
          NumBite, <strong>every digit counts.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="fact-options">
        <form action="/number" method="get">
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Number Fact</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/date" method="get">
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Date Fact</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/year" method="get">
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Year Fact</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/math" method="get">
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Math Fact</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </main>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
  </body>
</html>
